These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-1::.
City: edinburgh, miami, london, nizza, prague, venice, paris
 1. the person traveling to edinburgh is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to prague##5
 2. the person traveling to nizza is somewhere between the person traveling to venice and the person traveling to prague##7
 3. the person traveling to miami is somewhere between the person traveling to venice and the person traveling to edinburgh##7
 4. the person traveling to miami is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to london##5
 5. the person traveling to paris is not to the left of the person traveling to venice##8
 6. the person traveling to miami is in an odd position##4
 7. the person traveling to venice is on the left or right of the person traveling to nizza##3
 8. the person traveling to venice is somewhere between the person traveling to prague and the person traveling to paris##7
 9. the person traveling to london is not to the right of the person traveling to nizza##8
10. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3     |      4      |  5   |  6  |   7    |
| City   | prague | edinburgh | miami | london | nizza | venice | paris |

