.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-2::.
7 different games are played: go, poker, canasta, monopoly, snooker, bridge, whist
 1. the person playing bridge is the person playing bridge##1
 2. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the left of the person playing go##5
 3. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the right of the person playing poker##5
 4. the person playing poker is in an even position##4
 5. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
 6. the person playing monopoly is somewhere to the left of the person playing poker##5
 7. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
 8. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing whist##1
 9. the person playing whist is in an even position##4
10. the person playing snooker is not to the left of the person playing go##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |       5       |    6     |      7       |
| Game   | monopoly | poker | bridge | whist | canasta | go | snooker |

